-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-2-200x99.jpg.webp 200w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-2-500x246.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 2400px) 100vw, 2400px" />BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio – macitynet.it
Energia affidabile nel freddo estremo
Quando le temperature scendono sotto lo zero, la maggior parte delle stazioni di alimentazione al litio diventano inutilizzabili a causa della placcatura del litio. La Pioneer Na supera questo limite: si ricarica in sicurezza a -15°C senza bisogno di pre-riscaldamento e fornisce piena potenza (1.500 W) fino a -25°C. Mette a disposizione 9 prese e può alimentare stufette elettriche durante blackout invernali, tenere accese le luci in un rifugio di montagna e ricaricare i telefoni satellitari durante le spedizioni più difficili.
<img decoding="async" class="wp-image-1435973 size-full" title="BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio - macitynet.it" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3.jpg.webp" alt="BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio - macitynet.it" width="2400" height="1243" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3.jpg.webp 2400w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-480x249.jpg.webp 480w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-1600x829.jpg.webp 1600w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-1536x796.jpg.webp 1536w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-2048x1061.jpg.webp 2048w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-811x420.jpg.webp 811w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-696x360.jpg.webp 696w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-1068x553.jpg.webp 1068w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-1920x994.jpg.webp 1920w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-50x26.jpg.webp 50w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-75x39.jpg.webp 75w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-100x52.jpg.webp 100w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-200x104.jpg.webp 200w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-3-500x259.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 2400px) 100vw, 2400px" />BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio – macitynet.it
Progettata per sicurezza e durata
Le batterie al sodio non solo eccellono al freddo, ma offrono anche maggiore stabilità termica e meno rischio di surriscaldamento. Supportata dal sistema intelligente BLUETOPUS AI-BMS, la Pioneer Na è protetta contro sovraccarichi, cortocircuiti e altri rischi. Il suo guscio ignifugo in ABS+PC è testato contro le cadute da 1,2 metri, il 50% oltre lo standard del settore, resistendo a urti e sollecitazioni reali.
<img decoding="async" class="wp-image-1435974 size-full" title="BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio - macitynet.it" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4.jpg.webp" alt="BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio - macitynet.it" width="2400" height="1249" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4.jpg.webp 2400w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-480x250.jpg.webp 480w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-1600x833.jpg.webp 1600w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-1536x799.jpg.webp 1536w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-2048x1066.jpg.webp 2048w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-807x420.jpg.webp 807w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-696x362.jpg.webp 696w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-1068x556.jpg.webp 1068w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-1920x999.jpg.webp 1920w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-50x26.jpg.webp 50w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-75x39.jpg.webp 75w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-100x52.jpg.webp 100w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-200x104.jpg.webp 200w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-4-500x260.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 2400px) 100vw, 2400px" />BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio – macitynet.it
Ricarica veloce
Con una ricarica doppia da 1.900 W (AC + solare), la Pioneer Na passa da 0 all’80% in soli 35 minuti in condizioni normali (10-25°C), risultando ottima quindi per partenze dell’ultimo minuto o in situazioni di emergenza. E se non ci sono prese di corrente nei paraggi, nessun problema perché supporta la ricarica tramite alternatore in 1,9 ore con il caricatore Charger 1 in modo da essere subito pronta prima ancora di arrivare al campeggio.
Alta potenza, basso consumo
La Pioneer Na eroga 1.500 W di potenza per alimentare dispositivi come laptop, macchine del caffè e utensili. I campeggiatori invernali possono usarla anche con coperte termiche e prepararsi un caffè caldo nelle zone più fredde e remote. La modalità Power Lifting la porta a 2.250 W per usarla anche con cose come i bollitori elettrici. E con un consumo in standby di soli 1,5 W, spreca pochissima energia permettendo alla batteria di alimentare ad esempio un router da 12 W per 44 ore o uno speaker da 15 W per 37 ore.
<img decoding="async" class="wp-image-1435975 size-full" title="BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio - macitynet.it" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5.jpg.webp" alt="BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio - macitynet.it" width="2400" height="1244" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5.jpg.webp 2400w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-480x249.jpg.webp 480w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-1600x829.jpg.webp 1600w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-1536x796.jpg.webp 1536w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-2048x1062.jpg.webp 2048w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-810x420.jpg.webp 810w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-696x361.jpg.webp 696w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-1068x554.jpg.webp 1068w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-1920x995.jpg.webp 1920w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-50x26.jpg.webp 50w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-75x39.jpg.webp 75w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-100x52.jpg.webp 100w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-200x104.jpg.webp 200w,  https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/webp-express/webp-images/uploads/2025/10/Bluetti-Pioneer-Na-5-500x259.jpg.webp 500w" sizes="(max-width: 2400px) 100vw, 2400px" />BLUETTI Pioneer Na, la prima al mondo con batteria al sodio – macitynet.it
Energia verde per il pianeta
La Pioneer Na è progettata per durare: offre oltre 4.000 cicli di ricarica, pari a più di 10 anni di utilizzo anche in ambienti difficili. E grazie all’uso del sodio, un elemento pulito e disponibile in abbondanza, riduce la dipendenza dai metalli rari, offrendo una soluzione energetica più sostenibile e responsabile.
Prezzo e disponibilità
La BLUETTI Pioneer Na sarà disponibile esclusivamente sul sito ufficiale BLUETTI a partire dal 15 ottobre, al prezzo lancio di €899. Se vi interessa sappiate che potete usufruire di uno sconto extra del 10% utilizzando il codice PIONEERNA10 valido fino al 30 dicembre 2025.

